    The class Position defines a position, either longitude or latitude, in degrees, minutes and seconds.

    Description

    Implementation Invariants

     invariant       degree >= 0 && degree < 360
 invariant       minutes >= 0 && minutes < 60
 invariant       seconds >= 0 && seconds < 60
